  heroHeadline:
    'Websites that get Ilkley businesses more <em class="text-accent italic">enquiries</em>, more <em class="text-accent italic">bookings</em> and found on Google.',
  heroExcerpt:
    "I'm Steve — I design and build WordPress websites for service businesses in Ilkley and across West Yorkshire. Not templated, not outsourced. Strategy, design, build, launch, and ongoing care. All from one person who actually picks up the phone.",
  heroImage: "/images/steve-1.jpg",
  heroImageAlt: "Steve Marks - Web designer serving Ilkley businesses",

  // Results section
  resultsHeadline: "A site that works while you're busy serving customers.",
  resultsText:
    "The best websites do their job while you're doing yours. They answer questions before anyone picks up the phone, build trust before the first meeting, and turn strangers into enquiries without you lifting a finger. That's what I build for Ilkley businesses.",
  testimonialQuote:
